A little later, the witness, who probably didn't recognize the actress at first, saw Locklear pull up on a nearby road and get out of the car.
The witness was the one who called 911 because she was worried about Locklears.
When the police arrived, they found the actress sitting in her car, which was blocking the road.
'She seemed to be disoriented', so they took the officers to a special drug and alcohol testing centre.
"According to a police spokesman, the actress was cooperative, and excessive consumption of alcohol was ruled out from the start". "Following initial observations by officers, we believe Locklear was under the influence of an unknown drug", the spokesman said.
